import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'
import EmployeeRegistrationForm from '../createEmployee/EmployeeRegistrationForm'

import Header from '../header/Header'


const RoutesForEmployee =()=>{
    return(
        <Router>
            <Switch>

                <Route exact path= "/registration" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>

                <Route exact path= "/" component = {Header}/>

            </Switch>
        </Router>
    )
}
export default RoutesForEmployee
